what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, multi_dimension_prefetch: Isolated selective dimension filters (date, item, customer, customer_address) into materialized CTEs to create small hash tables before joining to the large fact table. Converted implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax for better optimizer planning. Kept the fact table filter (ss_wholesale_cost) and complex non-equi ZIP comparison in the main WHERE clause to avoid materializing unnecessary rows.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
